{"word":"ἐξοικίζω","slug":"ἐξοικίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐξοικίζω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> attic <el>ιῶ</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to remove</i> one <i>from his home, eject, banish</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> and <a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to go from home, remove, emigrate</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschines'>Aeschin.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to dispeople, empty</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}